page.title: 11SUTTON HOUSING, B'HAM
page.content: THE BACK DOOR LEADS INTO THE KITCHEN WHICH HAS A COOKER, FRIDGE-FREEZER, SINK, PINE TABLES AND PINE STORAGE CUPBOARDS. A WASHING MACHINE, TUMBLE DRIER AND SPIN DRIER ARE IN THE GARAGE. THE KITCHEN DOOR LEADS INTO THE SITTING ROOM WHICH HAS A DARK PINK CARPET, AN ITALIAN OAK TABLE AND MATCHING SIDEBOARD AND MIRROR. THERE IS A GAS FIRE WITH A SLATE FIREPLACE. THE SITTING ROOM ALSO HAS A DARK BROWN SETTEE, OTHER CUPBOARDS AND HANGING PLANTS BY THE STAIRS. THE PINK CARPET GOES UP THE STAIRS AND ACROSS THE LANDING. THE SAME COLOUR CARPET GOES INTO THE BACK ROOM WHICH HAS A SEPERATE ROOM FOR THE TOILET. THE HOUSE HAS THREE BEDROOMS, ONE OF THEM IS MINE, ONE IS MY BROTHERS AND MY PARENTS HAVE THE LARGEST BEDROOM.
